too my dear friends at sallys apizza   i ran into a friend mikey L last week and we talked about how we never used the front door at sallys  from the early sixtys when we were just little kids to the eightys  we talked about our street  and the people we grew up with  and iasked mike how aunt  flora was he said the last time he seen her  she looked good  she always let us in the kitchen door i just had a surgery and spent  the last week in bed and heard the terrible  news  my deepest thoughts and prayers too all of you  love  always bobby quartiano and family
